{"tid":1455432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場香港人 請即散！好危險！","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:41:19.000Z","uid":169109,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bb179eb6d4516f4b700e439c257ee6102d65bbf3","tid":1455432,"uid":169109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:01:01.000Z","msg":"Airport will be closed until midnight , all aircraft cannot arrive Hong Kong til midnight！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【逃生路線Forward<br />\nSend比所有係機場既朋友】<br />\n<br />\n機場T1 抵港大堂疏散路線<br />\n<br />\n藍線為大路，有機會被警察部防封鎖<br />\n紅線為緊急逃生路線，已查証可繼續通行！<br />\n<br />\n切記不要進入禁區,如需要出示passport及boarding pass的地方,因機場特警係可以合理執法。<br />\n唔可以再失去任何一個手足，大家小心<br />\n不受傷 不流血 不被捕<br />\n<br />\n#巴打提供<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Gn3Rtt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Gn3Rtt.png&h=6e990c8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：魚翅員工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CHoeX9g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCHoeX9g.png&h=7b4ffcbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已fact checked<br />\nAA sent message to all airline management.<br />\n今天餘下所有航班取消<br />\n已從外站起飛嘅航班有機會未能於香港國際機場降落<br />\n而未起飛嘅亦唔會俾clearance走<br />\nT1準備清完遊客就放TG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化<br />\n唔值再食TG<br />\n機場特警有權開真槍</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n速龍小隊入緊機場，有配催淚彈😰<br />\n剛才我地企左係通道邊 <br />\n有個空少行過黎同我地講 <br />\n有2~30個防暴同佢地一齊過關 而家匿左係免稅個度入面<br />\n有ptu入緊機場 fact checked<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GrpBr29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGrpBr29.png&h=1468fc45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3e67e9619d38f7a11290b4093ed1d5d9242d91","tid":1455432,"uid":169109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:01:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80a3634377d3aef3b0fc74a8409526c0cf21847f","tid":1455432,"uid":169109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"唔好睇個垃圾錄音記者會住！<br />\n不受傷！"},{"pid":"a9631d958ff86bedee69fd15e89f61ea4380cbee","tid":1455432,"uid":169109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:02:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化<br />\n唔值再食TG<br />\n機場特警有權開真槍</span></span>"},{"pid":"c858cb36e7633bd6569265bbd8061a031401d771","tid":1455432,"uid":75928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:02:46.000Z","msg":"推呀 十萬火急 唔值得<br />\n目標已成"},{"pid":"fd5cfa4aa8b08e40c9cb6d21b942617c38dabb96","tid":1455432,"uid":169109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:02:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化<br />\n唔值再食TG<br />\n機場特警有權開真槍</span></span>"},{"pid":"d443a24905bc816fafb7bd5d1b351759bcaef59c","tid":1455432,"uid":270276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:03:09.000Z","msg":"1) 而家已經無客, 你無宣傳既對象<br />\n2) 已經令航班取消"},{"pid":"3b443b508e449ca6b84aef01a12118969e57f31e","tid":1455432,"uid":169109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:03:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化<br />\n唔值再食TG<br />\n機場特警有權開真槍</span></span>"},{"pid":"b9b88713e7e0ff84d7af95d1b745a82c177b2091","tid":1455432,"uid":169109,"l